metadata.name: Circus Beast #0001
metadata.description:
Some people like buying clothes, some people like drinking, some people like cars, other people like clothes tailored to size, single barrel whiskey and Ferraris.

NFT's are just like clothes, drinks and cars.   You can choose to rock something that was made in bulk or, you can choose art that is handcrafted and made to your liking by a man who's been making art his entire life.

Circus Beast is a group of limited edition, hand crafted, custom sculpted and, custom painted  NFT's originally made from commissioned derivatives but, breaking off into an independent series of one of a kind sculptures.

(Full IP rights are granted only to the current owner of each NFT)
